                        <interp inst="t18350511-name-1384" type="surname" value="ROSE"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18350511-name-1384" type="given" value="ISAAC"></interp>ISAAC ROSE</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a salesman, and live in Tooley-street. On the 16th of April, between five and six o'clock in the evening, I saw the prisoner put his foot on my step, and reach these shoes, which hung over the door<lb></lb>way—he ran off with them—I pursued—he threw them away—I knew him well before, and did not trouble myself about him then, but gave information to a policeman, who took him the next day—I am posi<lb></lb>tive he is the man—I picked the shoes up.</p>
